0272,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"80ae5a2c08ad3409fda0f83d727398e16afe6c65","tid":2099761,"uid":115066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"479f3cc2505ac4fdc84697a4070fe8b32e4d8b66","tid":2099761,"uid":159266,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:33:06.000Z","msg":"閃靈根本過譽, David lynch每套驚悚片都好睇過閃靈好多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:42:42.000Z","msg":"好難比，david Lynch 詭異多過驚悚,過譽就難講，點先算過譽"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:54:32.000Z","msg":"Agree<br />\n點先算過譽?<br />\nDavid Lynch作品既元素當中有咁多不可被常理去理解既vision, <br />\n就算係鐘意佢作品既人, 都無可能可以用一個理性標準去評價佢既高低<br />\n咁同樣地, David Lynch作品既&quot;譽&quot;又點樣拿捏? <br />\n當如果有人話David Lynch係&quot;過譽&quot;, 你又可以用咩理性觀點去反駁呢?<br />\n我只係想講, 就咁掉&quot;過譽&quot;兩個字出黎去評價藝術, 其實無咩討論空間。<br />\n講到尾，藝術都係&quot;相對&quot; 概念黎。你起碼要掉你把尺出黎，大家先可以攞住你把尺同自己把尺黎討論, 比較。"},{"pid":"15f8a2d90d4c653c9974fe266ef46fe25e8e6c9b","tid":2099761,"uid":7878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182293b977c03ebb976db173dc951807739d301e","tid":2099761,"uid":169618,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"quote":{"pid":"b3aff8fdbc6765997a79f475dcee833265da94d8","tid":2099761,"uid":20272,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"81b1a9814194901a4fca4a27b40aec4fde8d5675","tid":2099761,"uid":20272,"like":41,"dislike":2,"score":39,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:23:10.000Z","msg":"第一, 佢係一套80年代既恐怖片, 你要諗返當年恐怖片既水平, 尤其係場景鏡頭上既處理成熟程度<br />\n<br />\nThe Shining 既空間感 (走廊, 房, 單點透視, 利用長鏡頭既處理),<br />\n=&gt; 做得好既恐怖片/電影, 係可以令你感受到場景中既地理, 你想像下當年既人戲院睇完, 行出戲院經過走廊既感覺。依種空間感，係好影響到近代恐怖片／電影既制作取態。<br />\n而當年黎講, 我好肯定無第二套恐怖片capture到依種咁subtle既恐怖感。<br />\n<br />\nThe Shining 既聲效 <br />\n=&gt; 最多人講就係細路踩單車, 經過地毯同木地板之間既聲音轉換, 你就會理解到係連地毯擺位都特登設計過<br />\n<br />\n劇本故事比較複雜有好多唔同觀眾/影評既演繹, 要再得閒先詳細討論"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:31:54.000Z","msg":"當然除咗劇本, 仲有好多technical既元素係The Shining入面都係處理得極為成熟<br />\n剪接, 聲效+配樂既互換運用, 色調, 鏡頭 都係擺返落現代都仲係完全唔老土。<br />\n講緊係40年前既戲呀大佬"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"其實成套戲最恐怖係女主角個樣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:56:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f97ab40459a1f9b2251a6acf0b27e520de7f01a3","tid":2099761,"uid":174601,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"2d517ea1e70680d5bfd9dd8ec9e9ffb0543a0994","tid":2099761,"uid":7043,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4f70074b8545a630a13f90c3fc87a4e288f32a23","tid":2099761,"uid":42007,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"顏色運用<br />\n氣氛形做<br />\n仲有配樂<br />\n唔係鳩嚇你，但你睇到好心寒"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:22:39.000Z","msg":"配樂我淨係覺得佢個high pitch noise 好刺耳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中後段個細路入房寫血字個陣唔知有冇播左成分鐘<br />\n刺耳到想熄聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:56:49.000Z","msg":"冇3D特效<br />\n個血池係依家有幾難做<br />\n以前美術、佈景全部心機野<br />\n依家乜都係電腦執"},{"pid":"89ff1aa1638efb296e934e94d2dfad95d4dce7fb","tid":2099761,"uid":52468,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:57:00.000Z","msg":"女主角個表情世界級，完全能夠代入佢果陣有幾驚嚇"},{"pid":"9c0da72dfaeb3da28606e734e05ed24a524c9dcc","tid":2099761,"uid":4780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f70074b8545a630a13f90c3fc87a4e288f32a23","tid":2099761,"uid":42007,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:18:31.000Z","msg":"顏色運用<br />\n氣氛形做<br />\n仲有配樂<br />\n唔係鳩嚇你，但你睇到好心寒"},"ci