<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20191109/MKGEDFVJUY2CIGQQGLTSIHMGUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20191109%2FMKGEDFVJUY2CIGQQGLTSIHMGUY%2F&d=68p4wiGQQ1h%2Fwz3iobjDKw2CFyCB1h158poew6f0R2E%3D&h=dbcb8b3d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20191109%2FMKGEDFVJUY2CIGQQGLTSIHMGUY%2F&h=cac0b5ce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20191109/MKGEDFVJUY2CIGQQGLTSIHMGUY/</a><br />\n至於飾演積尼高遜（Jack Nicholson）太太的女主角Shelley Duvall，現已淡出影壇多年，3年前她上電視受訪透露自己患上精神疾病：「我病得很重，我需要幫助。」讓外界唏噓不已。當年導演寇比力克不斷改劇本，還刻意在片場孤立Shelley，並與她不斷爭執，Shelley單是拍攝拿着棒球棒與積尼高遜對峙的鏡頭，就拍了127次，讓她真真正正的精神崩潰，她在收工後甚至對導演出示一團掉下來的頭髮球，讓他知道自己所承受了極大壓力。"},{"pid":"d9ab7f45db98142d4a08091638b927fb18e07f67","tid":2099761,"uid":114875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8479ae65d1b82201b6113983f79dffccdcaa9301","tid":2099761,"uid":354042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"a8efd65eb276b158aa6ccdea15bd0f174392802e","tid":2099761,"uid":114875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"182293b977c03ebb976db173dc951807739d301e","tid":2099761,"uid":169618,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:45:49.000Z","msg":"其實成套戲最恐怖係女主角個樣"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:13:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T14:25:53.000Z","msg":"女主角係俾導演嚇到痂左...<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />.<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20191109/MKGEDFVJUY2CIGQQGLTSIHMGUY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2F