=\"hkgmoji\" />，我自己比較係比佢既奇幻風格吸引"},{"pid":"5d570f719b093a44b984ccb96d08502b877a8500","tid":2099761,"uid":158711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6df98db3b6dcbab9ddd9977eebed9ae4d128b7b","tid":2099761,"uid":19252,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:52:09.000Z","msg":"搭單問 沉默的羔羊 又點睇？<br />\n除咗Anthony Hopkins 神演技外，我唔係咁識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T17:03:42.000Z","msg":"見到呢個post我都想講， 睇完真係唔明點解咁多人話好睇"},{"pid":"72ca36a9e6a2b33911e3d5e1c457804f3623f931","tid":2099761,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"95d0e6b718312884e6a864782b4c8e61f5c201f5","tid":2099761,"uid":99493,"like":21,"dislike":1,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:36:37.000Z","msg":"又有人出嚟challenge經典舊片<br />\n<br />\n你而家睇star wars<br />\n都會一路睇一路屌<br />\n<br />\n諗下人哋1979年上映<br />\n四十一年前<br />\n當其時幾震撼"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T21:08:01.000Z","msg":"問下點解又唔係否定佢<br />\n邊到有challenge<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b48b8f4201077c9413ff4e1a1aec5107aa14866","tid":2099761,"uid":39215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T21:10:41.000Z","msg":"一樣 覺得幾好睇<br />\n但未係神作<br />\n<br />\n話好心寒個班係咪小小野都驚個類人?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8765504391d6a84230078f0068c9ded64677b6c7","tid":2099761,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ec07e97a9d01f03b2c22306cc1c77397bd105ee","tid":2099761,"uid":359151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b22510bffcb7abbe9919288f82db43304f5c08e","tid":2099761,"uid":7043,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T13:07:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩睇完覺得悶到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n定係我唔識欣賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/n